<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1191.110418.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Rhopalothrix amati paratype worker (IAvH- 55018) A full-face view B lateral view C dorsal view D portion of the head viewed obliquely showing the mandibles and the apical fork of the left mandible; the black arrow points to the subapical tooth while the white one points to the apical tooth of the apical fork of the mandible. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/983270" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

